    "However, each of these factors is conducted separately in individual studies, and the corresponding studies focus mostly on boom periods, which are not necessarily transferable to the bust period from November 2021 to the end of 2022, during which Bitcoin and major CCs declined by more than 75%.",
    "This study focused only on Bitcoin and Ethereum, commonly used in the related literature for several reasons.",
    "Bitcoin and Ethereum are the two largest CCs in terms of market capitalization.",
